name: JAM (just another merge)
description:
Just another merge of some popular models, that I think turned out good.

It's somewhere between 2.5d and realistic. The merge is a bit biased towards nudity, blonde hair and asian looks, but is still pretty versatile. (see example images)

There is no VAE baked in, so I suggest using either vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.vae.ckpt or kl-f8-anime2.ckpt with the merge.

The merge works well with either clip skip 1 or 2.

Changelog:

Update 1.5

  • added model darksun

  • added LoRA "Add More Details"

  • resulting in increased contrast and details

  • Negative should include: (worst quality:1.0), (low quality:1.0), (bad-picture-chill-75v:0.9), bad-hands-5

Added inpainting version of 1.4b

Update 1.4b

  • jam v1.4 + some nextphoto v1.0

  • style didn't change much, but faces are more realistic and the merge is less biased towards nudity or blonde hair

Update 1.4

  • Replaced fantasticmix with schExcelsior. The model was getting too realistic, now it's more even between 2.5d and realistic.

  • Merged realisticVaginasGod_godpussy1V2 into the model.

  • Breasts/Nipples are more consistent now, pussy is still a bit random.

  • Can't do old people -.- trying to fix that with then next version.

Update 1.2:

  • Added fantasticmix_v50 to the merge, now it should be a bit more flexible with fantasy/sci-fi stuff.

  • Accessories, like necklaces, also are seemingly more consistent.

Updated models in v1.1:

  • uberRealisticPornMerge_urpmv13

  • henmixReal_v30

  • cyberrealistic_v21

  • revAnimated_v122
